        <div class="contents">
          <ul>
            <li>
              <b>Students:</b> Our students have proven themselves at school
              level as well as getting through the cutthroat nationwide
              competitive JEE examinations.
            </li>
            <br />
            <li>
              <b>Faculty & Curriculum:</b> Over 80% of our faculty are PhDs
              and are actively involved in journal publications and research
              projects. With such experienced professors at the helm and our
              unique design-centric curriculum, our students graduate with
              strong technical expertise and a holistic approach to solving
              real-world problems.
            </li>
            <br />
            <li>
              <b>Industrial Experience:</b> Students are exposed to a 5 month
              internship programme where they are encouraged to be part of the
              decision making process in all aspects of product development,
              from business to design to technology with an option to pursue
              it in the Instituteâ€™s in-house incubator MadeIT also. This gives
              them an extra edge when being recruited as they can adapt much
              more quickly to their respective careers.
            </li>
            <br />
            <li>
              <b>Balanced Personas:</b> Students are given the freedom to set
              up their own respective societies and clubs based on their
              passions and express their form of art be it in science,
              technology or culture.
            </li>
          </ul>
